If a user mistype or the page does not exist then the script will search queries through the site and return the result

Hi all, does anyone know if it's possible to create Marketplace templates using COS and custom modules rather than template builder?
<@U22PKFRU5> <@U22PU4G4A> <@U22PJPGK0> <@U22VBL87M> any word if the ability to add/move/rename more folders is coming to the COS or ftp anytime soon?
hey <@U26CZR9MW> it’s something we’re definitely considering but not actively working on at the moment
no problem — if you’d like to give specific feedback on your use case or what you need, feel free to ping me directly and I can share with the team that will be working on it

A simple request really, instead of Coded Files > Custom > page > OnlyOneLevelOptionHereRightNow_folder

something like this would be nice (editable via the COS & FTP):
Coded Files > Custom > page > FolderWeNowHaveAcessTo > 1MoreFolder > LastFolderOption > MaybeJust1MoreFolderButYouDecide

We know from the community, many others are looking for even more levels, but the flexibility of even just 1 or 2 more folder levels would go a LONG way in helping us stay organized 

T.Y.I.A.
